summary: An Ordinance accepting a deed from J. J. Soper and Mary E. Soper, his wife, to the City of Seattle, dated the 13th day of June, 1904 to Lots Twenty three (23) and Twenty-four (24) in Block Eleven (11) and Lots Eleven (11), Twelve (12), Thirteen (13) and Fourteen (14) in Block Twelve (12) of Hazelwood Addition Supplemental, all in the City of Seattle. To be used for park purposes.
